snippet.textDisplay: Pakistan is my country. And I am proud of it. I have a small message for Pakistanis here. Please just keep on loving this country. Just try to correct yourself in all aspects  of life. Things will get better. We will succeed. We will make this country what our Father of the nation Muhammad Ali Jinnah wanted it to be. Just don't lose hope.
